{"tid":534072,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱坐緊地鐵，有個廢老逼我讓座。。。","createTime":"2018-01-19T12:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T17:47:35.000Z","uid":143699,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2471957a65bcee78c8fba65c12bfd943700e97cc","tid":534072,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:21:05.000Z","msg":"話說啱啱收工，攰到就暈低，快快手上地鐵返屋啦。一入到去，即刻見到個空位，我二話不說，雙腳快速擺動，將同座位短短四個身位既距離迅間拉近。就係我坐咗落去之後。。。<br />\n<br />\n廢老：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「㗩！」<br />\n<br />\n有個廢老企咗係我面前，用一幅死人嘴臉望住我<br />\n<br />\n我見狀馬上閉合雙眼，裝作低頭休息<br />\n<br />\n「㗩！」<br />\n<br />\n怎料到個廢老竟然係都唔放過我，繼續試圖用呢啲死人聲音騷擾我<br />\n<br />\n我終於按捺不住<br />\n<br />\n「喂，伯伯，你㗩夠未啊？好嘈啊！」<br />\n<br />\n我對他呼喝道，在車箱中所有的目光都轉移到我和廢老身上<br />\n<br />\n「喂，後生仔，你都唔知訂既，叫你讓個位嚟坐啊！」<br />\n<br />\n廢老馬上反擊<br />\n<br />\n我冷笑一聲，說<br />\n<br />\n「啱啱放工好攰啊，不了！」<br />\n<br />\n我絲毫不動，完全沒有打算讓坐<br />\n<br />\n「哇，睇下依家啲後生仔啦，都唔識尊重老人家」<br />\n<br />\n廢老竟然故意提高聲線，意圖吸引所有人的注意力，利用群眾的目光逼使我讓座<br />\n<br />\n廢老果然高招。。。"},{"pid":"0e96b82cc5d53f6dd90c4d20bd061d8208485f55","tid":534072,"uid":160032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:28:24.000Z","msg":"我會繼續訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f199e33ba53116bf525c80f949a373bb86a40f","tid":534072,"uid":143699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:31:47.000Z","msg":"條廢老的策略果然起到效果，車箱內既乘客開始有反應<br />\n<br />\n「讓個位比老人家坐姐。。。咁都唔肯既。。。」<br />\n<br />\n「咪係囉。。。呢啲後生仔真係唔要得。。。」<br />\n<br />\n乘客們都紛紛低聲議論著<br />\n<br />\n廢老嘴角一揚，明顯因爲自己既計謀成功而得意。<br />\n<br />\n「哼！讓位啦𡃁仔！」<br />\n<br />\n廢老囂張的對著我說<br />\n<br />\n「哈哈哈哈！！！！」<br />\n<br />\n我突然仰頭大笑"},{"pid":"d4b66f7be4f6c5a40510ccb0657243fab8d9c772","tid":534072,"uid":134683,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"搭輕鐡試過兩次<br />\n應該係同一個阿伯黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢直接拍醒我叫我讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次我求其喺公事包攞張醫院假紙話我都係傷殘叫佢過關愛座<br />\n第二次直接指佢過關愛座講都廢撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩次都知衰自己行開冇你呢個咁頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca49949481f4a08fac623db0cf5ed2f40e23ba20","tid":534072,"uid":130955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:46:01.000Z","msg":"唔讓啦梗係，兩蚊搭地鐵仲想點<br />\n後生仔比咁貴車費<br />\n位都冇得坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09407ce82b9c17c3df9e2862498eae61cff95cb","tid":534072,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4b66f7be4f6c5a40510ccb0657243fab8d9c772","tid":534072,"uid":134683,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"搭輕鐡試過兩次<br />\n應該係同一個阿伯黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢直接拍醒我叫我讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次我求其喺公事包攞張醫院假紙話我都係傷殘叫佢過關愛座<br />\n第二次直接指佢過關愛座講都廢撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩次都知衰自己行開冇你呢個咁頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:47:01.000Z","msg":"我唔好彩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b9048095732ed0f0d841b24100f8fbdf3f5ad7","tid":534072,"uid":99048,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:47:32.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈哈哈！<br />\n阿伯你太天真喇，其實我係跛㗎<br />\n<br />\n哈哈哈哈哈！<br />\n<br />\n完！"},{"pid":"e1e198722c2c5ea6926adfb7ddc28de7497ebb4a","tid":534072,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭輕鐡試過兩次<br />\n應該係同一個阿伯黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢直接拍醒我叫我讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次我求其喺公事包攞張醫院假紙話我都係傷殘叫佢過關愛座<br />\n第二次直接指佢過關愛座講都廢撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩次都知衰自己行開冇你呢個咁頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>佢唔好彩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc71dfb95cb2645e7e8660e06654127757946e82","tid":534072,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"「想我讓座？？？慳啲啦！」<br />\n<br />\n我狂妄地對指著著廢老說<br />\n<br />\n眾人都被我的怪異舉指所嚇到，連廢老都為之一驚<br />\n<br />\n「你。。。你起身呀！」<br />\n<br />\n廢物為了面子，已經不顧儀態，佢試圖直接拉住我既衣袖，把我從座位上拉下來<br />\n<br />\n但是<br />\n<br />\n我！穩！如！泰！山！<br />\n<br />\n廢老明顯被自己的笨拙舉動弄得一臉尷尬，連臉面都漸漸開始出現通紅<br />\n<br />\n「哈哈哈哈！」<br />\n<br />\n「你拉得郁我咪比你坐囉！」<br />\n<br />\n我神色自若地坐在座位上，對著廢老嘲笑道。<br />\n<br />\n車箱內氣氛異常奇怪。。。"},{"pid":"91d4b126c89806076f66fd86839d2108956822ec","tid":534072,"uid":124899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dYqW7UdFDcY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdYqW7UdFDcY&d=OTMKY0medqEF%2Bc%2Bl%2F%2FVY1U%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2c3de878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dYqW7UdFDcY</a>"},{"pid":"3f41bb13c4a3a711390642949c1aac153829216d","tid":534072,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:03:36.000Z","msg":"就在僵持不下的情況下，異變突起<br />\n<br />\n廢老拉扯著我的右手傳來一股陰勁，我一時大意，整個人被拉出座位外，在失去平衡下更不小心絆倒在地上。<br />\n<br />\n我目光驚訝的看著廢老<br />\n<br />\n他。。。會功夫嗎？<br />\n<br />\n「哼！」<br />\n<br />\n廢老一臉不屑的望著我，緩緩的坐了在我的座位上。<br />\n<br />\n我怎麼也料不到，一個厚顏無恥的廢老，竟然是個會功夫的老人。。。這下我也是以貌取人了。<br />\n<br />\n要說最驚訝的，車箱內一群乘客更是目瞪口呆，一個看似弱不禁風的老人，上一秒被人羞辱著，下一秒卻是輕鬆的將人擊到。<br />\n<br />\n我坐在地上，還在慢慢消化著這突如其來的狀況"},{"pid":"4ba8d39f938ea1eb54c3b5c802266763a6cf0070","tid":534072,"uid":38788,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:15:04.000Z","msg":"其實你比我地討論仲好過你係到作故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da03bc41a9c35dc026c5b9e8f3df9a9b094b70c","tid":534072,"uid":57410,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:17:22.000Z","msg":"屌你 家下騙徒手法層出不窮 最撚憎小說"},{"pid":"c33a1a41230f338dcecc7e258698a71f7a16b8c8","tid":534072,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:29:26.000Z","msg":"太羞人了，我竟然被人個廢老擊到在地上，強忍住羞恥心，我用公司包擋住自己的臉，眼框中的淚水洶湧而出，太可惡啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n我緩緩的從地上站起來，無視著他人的目光，走到車箱的閘門前，只求下一個站快點到來，好讓我離開這個地方，我實在太丟人了。。。<br />\n<br />\n從閘門的倒影中，看著自己一臉淚痕和不堪的面容，我實在是很痛心。經過一整天疲累的工作，不單在公司被老闆三翻四次的辱罵，連放工後都要被廢老羞辱，我的人生。。。太差勁了"},{"pid":"0fac7e1b101c246c33f12db19cd130e44f177c69","tid":534072,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:46:31.000Z","msg":"碌撚上左癈老身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f857bef892d49bdac1b077cf5ec044085d8a59f9","tid":534072,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:59:51.000Z","msg":"新文G持 留名睇佢比廢老屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064adf2f6e5ab95c839bd141071171974049e8c7","tid":534072,"uid":25619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"然後，我上連登出post，等大家笑多次，完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88d74cb0083e7846a52f2800448c19d21d991a0","tid":534072,"uid":143699,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T15:59:19.000Z","msg":"真係真人真事，唔係故嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset